Notes: UWW ranked 24th in the NCAA Div. III...UWO snaps 12-game losing streak to UWW
...UWW built 18-7 lead with 6:45 left in the first half...UWO goes on 18-4 run
to take a 45-38 lead with 4:11 remaining...After UWW cuts deficit to 50-49,
UWO gets two free throws by Kitzke and Wenig in the final 22 seconds.
Game.Officials: Larry Dietz,  Erin Rickard,  Joe Steiber
